headline: Wall Street Lunch: Nvidia CEO Huang Confirms Investment In Musk's XAI
summary: Nvidia (NVDA) CEO Jensen Huang confirmed that his company has invested in the latest funding round for Elon Musk's generative artificial intelligence outfit xAI (X.AI).
